            Bio
            Hi , I’m Enow Jane, a nurse, trained business and
            wellness oriflame coach, and consultant . I bring to you
            PURE DERMA « nourish to Blossom » a well known brand which
            is out to solve skin related issues , lose weight ,stay fit
            and Also help people start up a business with oriflame.
            My goal is to make you look great by using our very
            authentic cosmetic products, have fun, and make
            money with ORIFLAME.
            
            
            Education
            Biaka University Institute of Buea |
            Buea, Cameroon
            BSc. Nursing | October 2018 - August 2022
